The OKF bundle visualizer in this directory is derived from the Open Knowledge
Format reference implementation:

  https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/knowledge-catalog
  okf/src/enrichment_agent/viewer/  (Apache License 2.0)

- templates/viz.html, static/viz.css, static/viz.js — vendored verbatim.
- generator.py — adapted: parses frontmatter with know's own store.parse_md
  (no enrichment_agent dependency), uses know's concept-type palette, and
  returns the HTML as a string for on-demand serving.

